pageProduct.description:
General Information

Amazonia Raw Protein Collagen Plus is a premium blend of Marine Collagen and organic sprouted and fermented plant protein. It supports daily protein intake, collagen production and connective tissue structure. A digestive enzyme blend and 5000mg of highly bioavailable Type I & III Collagen Peptides promote easy absorption. With wholefood Vitamin C and Zinc to support hair, skin and nails, Raw Protein Collagen Plus is the ultimate beauty protein.

Warnings

Contains Fish

Common Uses

Protein Shakes, Protein Balls, Cooking,  Smoothies, Breakfast Bowls.

Ingredients

Organic Sprouted & Fermented Golden Pea Protein*, Marine Collagen, Organic Cocoa Powder*, Natural Flavours, Organic Stevia Leaf Extract*, Digestive Enzyme (Bromelain), Wildcrafted Sea Buckthorn Juice, Monk Fruit Extract. *Certified Organic
